window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With one look, Brooke knows that she cant fight the desire that pulled them together before, despite the skeletons in both their closets.</p> <p>Leif Montgomery fell hard for Brooke Alder in Paris when they were young, and he thought their fling was just an early taste of what life had in store for him.</p> <p>But life had other plans, and he didn't find that kind of love—or see Brookes face—for years.</p> <p>Until he visits his cousins house and sees whos moved in next door.</p> <p>They've both changed: she's a struggling single mom, he's running from a past he's trying to hide while opening up a new tattoo shop. Yet the moment he sees her again, he knows she's the one for him.</p>"; 
